CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778256667
OL,3,CGreen Party's Zoe Garbett elected as
OL,4,Cnew Hackney Mayor
OL,6,FMr Polanski was speaking to reporters
OL,7,Fin Hackney, where the Greens won a
OL,8,Fdecisive victory in the contest for
OL,9,Fthe directly-elected mayor of the
OL,10,Fborough.
OL,12,F"My message to Keir Starmer is it's
OL,13,Ftime to go," the Green leader said.
OL,15,F"The country has clearly rejected you.
OL,16,FI think he'd been rejected before
OL,17,Fthese elections even started.
OL,19,F"We had 14 years of Conservative
OL,20,Fausterity.
OL,26,@kD@QxrtD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
